CharmLU -- Dense LU Factorization

Computes and validates the factorization of an N x N matrix.

Running:
./charmrun +p4 ./charmlu 512 64 500 128 3 1 4 2 2

Argument list:
Matrix size
Block size
Memory threshold
Pivot batch size
Mapping scheme (3 for block-cyclic)
Block-cyclic tile rows
Block-cyclic tile cols
Block-cyclic tile rotate
Block-cyclic tile stride